imdb.plot outline: After a night of heavy drinking, Dom wakes up to find his life turned upside down when the discovery of a dead body in his kitchen leads him to think he's the murderer. Desperate to cover any trace of the bloody mess before his girlfriend returns home, Dom enlists the help of his idiotic best friend, Roger Swanson, and the two set forth a plan of action only to discover things are far worse than they could possibly have imagined. ...The Dead Are Coming Back to Life.
